{"tid":355533,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"經紀呃阿婆北韓會開戰 46萬積蓄炒倫敦金輸晒","createTime":"2017-08-11T11:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T11:18:30.000Z","uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a77cf2fbba3de93ef91ecc77fd599fb18ea610cd","tid":355533,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:06:35.000Z","msg":"年屆63歲的事主陳婆婆（化名）今年3月開始接聽時代金業的湯先生「cold call」，起初未有答應投資，惟湯生不斷用電話轟炸又建議可遷就在任何地點傾談，又稱已任職該公司6年有豐富經驗<br />\n<br />\n最終二人於3月底在西九龍中心一間食肆見面。當日湯帶來數張紙予事主簽署，聲稱北韓一連串動作顯示「一定會打仗」，強調「你唔賺大把人賺」，又指若事主賺錢後可捐予無國界醫生做善事，成功說服她授權投資並存入6萬元。惟其後事主收到公司寄來包裹，已簽署的文件竟被加添十多頁條款一併釘裝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170811/57035976\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170811%2F57035976&d=LqU%2Biehar3Y0COcM%2FKLbcAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=182574f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170811%2F57035976&h=86280ea2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170811/57035976</a>"},{"pid":"5832c7d9a2c7fd852d59f293cba16f870560dbf1","tid":355533,"uid":62842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:12:06.000Z","msg":"呢d真係畜生不如<br />\n雖則廢老自己都有責任"},{"pid":"b334aeb19ccc26a172485125daa87491f626bda9","tid":355533,"uid":101976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"都係嗰句<br />\n倫敦金死全家"}]}